Comment:
Sana lang makamit nang mga Indian farmers ang hustisya? Pls lng po kayong mga gobyerno unahin po ninyo ang mga consumer na bigyan halaga? Wag yong puro mga salitan nang mga technology sa ibat ibang bansa? Kasi po napaka hirap maging farmers dahil halos hingiin ninyo ang kanilang producto samangtalang pag nasa merkado at exportation na ang mga pananim nila sagad po kayo kung kumita?
Ngayon ko maranasan lahat para sigiro malaman ko kung paano balansihin lahat? Unahin ang mga pagkain sa hapag kainan at bigyan sila nang halaga? Yan po kay langan nila? Sa ngayon pinapanood ko kung paano mag trabaho ang mga farmers kung anong halaga sa kanila bilang isang farmers. Dito ko makikita ang mga batang sampo pataas kung paano sila tumulong sa kanilang mga magulang para lang may pambili nang mga kay langan nila sa paaralan? Nakita ko kung paano sila maging masaya at nakikita mo sa kanilang mga mata ang pag asa para lng maka tapos sila sa paaralan? Nung araw ayaw ko king anong buhay talaga meron ako at mas pinili ang simple at masayang buhay na walang ibang obligation kundi ang pamilya? Pero mas magaling parin ang ating ama sa langit dahil habang inaayawan at gusto kong iwan lalo niya akong pinapahirapan gamit ang aking pamilya? Masaya at mas maswerte ang mga farmers kasama ang kanilang pamilya na nag bubungkal nang kanilang lupain samantalang kami pilit na tinatakasan at iniiba pero hinihila nang panahon at ngayon oras at araw na lang ang pagitan sa amin bilang isang farmers? Sana lang po bigyan halaga po sila dahil maging dito sa pinas tingin nang gobyerno silay mababa at walang kwentang farmers lamang? Next yr pinas isang masaganang ani ang meron sa lahat pero sana naman wag puro negosiyante ang kumikita? Kasi po 36 per kilo ang bigas sa mercado samantalng ang bili po nila sa mga farmers 7 pesos lamang. Sana gawing 17 perkilo to 20 at wagnang bumaba sa proseyo nito

Name: Amaravathi Iyer
Comment: This is a politically driven protest. Punjab ruled by Congress Govt has instigated it's farmers. These are farmers who've voted congress. PM's explanation innumerable times on how farmers will be benefitted & how the bill will stop the middlemen from looting farmers has gone to deaf ears as these farmers continue to support for Congress. The farmers from other states are happy with the Govt's bill except Punjab run by Congress Govt. Why do farmers only from Punjab have a problem with the new bill when the farmers from other states are happy with the new bill? After 70 years of slavery & Muslim rule, for the first time India has been gifted with a nationalist leader like Shri Narendra Modi who's transforming India to be a developed country competing with the top most countries in the world, appreciated by the top level leaders of the world. Farmers protest is a conspiracy of the Congress to defame Modi's Govt & to loot our Indian farmers through the anti national elements called The middlemen. The farmers of India are against the farmers of Punjab for their politically driven protest. The punjab farmers have blocked 5 national highways due to which commuters are finding difficulty to travel for their work. And the aggressive & ruthless Punjab farmers are asking working people to join their politically driven protest. You're farmers you grow your own ration, but people of the country get their ration from the salary they get from their work place. Will you Punjab farmers pay salary for the comman man for his food, for his children's education, for his rent & medical expenses of the elderly. You want common man to spoil the lives of his family members & join your politically driven protest. When Punjab farmers do not want to understand the common man's suffering created by them &  do not want to understand the Govt's stand on helping to benefit the farmers of our country, why should the Govt agree to your demands? Agreeing to the demands of Punjab farmers is murdering the benefits of the farmers of this great country India. It's time farmers from different states come together & protest against the Punjab farmers & stop them from getting the benefits of Indian farmers ruined. The attitude of Punjab farmers, display their adamant stand in support of their Congress rulers who rule their state, The farmers from the states ruled by BJP are happy with this new bill for they understand it's benefits towards them. Hindus will never forgive Punjab farmers for misleading the world against our PM Modi & against our Govt. Why don't the farmers from other states want to join the Punjab farmers protest? Because they know that Punjab farmers protest is not against the bill but it's against Modi & BJP Govt. I want the people from different countries to understand that India is not facing farmers protest but India is facing only Punjab farmers protest. Please understand & investigate, the farmers throughout India are happy with Modi's bill. This unruly protest is only from Punjab farmers & Punjab is currently ruled by Congress. It's time for the farmers of India who are happy with the new farmers bill to voice out & protest against the politically driven Punjab farmers. Jai Jawan Jai KIsan of India. Jai Hind!

Name: Sammu Dada
Comment:
Adani, Ambani and other corporates had an eye on massive food grain market of India. They had few problems:

Problem 1 :
States had different rules and regulations to buy food grains from farmers. It was difficult for corporates to handle so many states with so many different regulations and taxes

Modi Solution:
Took control from states and made 1 act for whole country. Corporates happy now.

Problem 2:
Corporates will buy crops and store them. But Essential Commodity act will stop them for storing crops for long time, as it increase prices in market.

Modi Solution:
Food crops will not come under Essential Commodity act and can be stored for longer period. Corporates again happy.

Problem 3
It was hard to determine that what type of crop will be grown by farmers.

Modi Solution:

Contract farming for farmers where they will be told by corporates to grow what kind of crop. Corporates again happy.

Problem 4 :

How Corporates will handle court cases if anything goes wrong against farmers.

Modi Solution:

Farmers can not go to courts. They will go to SDM and DC.
Corporates again happy as they can bribe them

They say bills are in favor of farmers. .... üôÅ
